-No, honey, because I love you,

87
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:09,240
I won’t let you drive like this when you’re sick.
-You said I’m not sick.

88
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:11,400
You said I am.
-Ugh.

89
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,520
Come on, come warm up a bit.

90
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:15,880
Just be careful not to overheat.

91
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,760
Shabbat Shalom.
-Shabbat Shalom.

92
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:21,240
Shabbat Shalom, Shabbat Shalom.

93
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,920
Shabbat Shalom.
-Shabbat Shalom.

94
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:26,400
Shabbat Shalom. How are you?
-We’re okay,

95
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:28,320
the baby was sick and just yesterday he got better.

96
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:30,920
Oh, right, if you don’t want him to get sick again,

97
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:35,640
keep him away from Shai because Shai’s in the kitchen and he’s sick.

98
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:36,760
Sick?
-Yeah.

99
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:39,360
Alin, sweetie, wouldn’t it be better to go home?
-Come on, don’t exaggerate,

100
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,400
we’ll keep me away from Shai, and that’s it.
-Okay, it’s your responsibility.

101
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:44,440
When does Shai need to leave the kitchen?
-You know that generally,

102
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:47,680
Shai doesn’t leave kitchens easily.
-Stay with him?

103
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,320
Shabbat Shalom.
-Shabbat Shalom, Mom.

104
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,440
Shabbat Shalom, Rachel.
-Shabbat Shalom.

105
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:53,120
Meirav’s in her room. She wants you to come in.

106
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:55,280
What does she want?
-No, she’s got some bug in her head

107
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:58,280
that she’s not coming back from abroad,
so she’s having wrap-up talks with everyone.

108
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,600
And she can’t do them from Los Angeles?

109
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,680
Because I see the computer’s outside.
What, are you talking to Efrat today?

110
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:04,280
Right, and I want you to help me
put it together, I can’t manage.

111
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:07,200
Later. Go, wash something here first.
-I’m really worried

112
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:09,760
about the germs Shai’s spreading in the air,
but on the other hand,

113
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:11,800
